description:
Prepare to be amazed by Keith Barry's brand new TV3 series. Keith Barry: Brain Hacker is an intelligent and inspirational show, which attempts to break into the minds of the audience with truly astonishing results.

This incredible six-part series takes the audience on a theatrical roller-coaster ride, where they participate in astounding feats based around mind control, including hypnosis and remote viewing.




Keith Barry: Brain Hacker - Series 1, Episode 1



Intuition

The renowned mentalist focuses on intuition as he tries to astound a studio audience comprising twins and triplets. Keith is joined by martial arts weapons experts, Keith Flynn, a highly poisonous gaboon viper snake and the Grandfather of mentalism David Berglas.




Original Air Date: 12-Jan-2014
